Description
PT Loista Indonesia We are a dynamic and fast growing Interior and Furnishing company that located in Serpong area, Tangerang, is looking for a highly motivated and qualified candidate for the position as.
Job Description :
Design Concept and Design Development Coordination and Preparation of Design Proposal to clients as per request and needs, include measuring the fields Preparation of Drawing Works Able to handle project independently from design conceptualization/ development till completion if needed.
Requirements
Minimum Diploma or Degree in Interior Design Fresh Graduate are welcomed Proven creative flair, strong color sense and design documentation Excellent space planning skills Proficiency in AutoCAD, 3DMax, Vray, Adobe Photoshop A good team player, committed, highly motivated Positive working attitude, good initiative and willing to learn Possess good communication and interpersonal skills Placement : Tangerang
All applications will be treated confidentially & only short listed candidates will be notified
Please click "Apply Now" button to apply
